<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wealth" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wealth,</orth> 1) welfare, prosperity: <cit><quote>I once did lend my body for his w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 249</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this is the imposthume of much w. and peace,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 4, 27</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) riches: <bibl n="shak. luc 17" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 17" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 17</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 29.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 29, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.37.5" default="NO" valid="yes">37, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.67.13" default="NO" valid="yes">67, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.75.4" default="NO" valid="yes">75, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.91.2" default="NO" valid="yes">91, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 270" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 270</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 2, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.362" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 362</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.362" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 362</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.232" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 232</bibl> <cit><quote>(the w. of Windsor Castle).</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 6</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 6</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 5.8.5" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 8</bibl>. 49 <cit><quote>(lost much w.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 70</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.149" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 149</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.257" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 257</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.5.62" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 62</bibl> <cit><quote>(the whole w. of thy wit).</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.269" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 269</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.269" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 269</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.269" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 269</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.173.269" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 173</bibl> <cit><quote>(for the w. that the world masters).</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.136" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 136</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>(get our jewels and our w. together).</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.5.54" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 54</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.5.84" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 5, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 1, 131</bibl> <cit><quote>(for the w. of all the world).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.280" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 280</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>(were masters of their w.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 46</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 5, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.82" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.23" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 10, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 8, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.284" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 284</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.495" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 495</bibl> <cit><quote>(whilst this poor w. lasts).</quote> <bibl n="sh